{% extends "layout_project.njk" %}
{% block content %}
    {% from "_components.njk" import iframeVideo %}
    <div class = "text-center">
        <h2 class="section-heading text-uppercase">3D Printed Robotic Hand</h2>
        <p class="item-intro text-muted">A robotic hand that mimics the user</p>
    </div>
    <div id="carouselHand" class="carousel slide" data-ride="carousel">
        <!-- Indicators -->
        <ol class="carousel-indicators">
            <li data-target="#carouselHand" data-slide-to="0" class="active"></li>
            <li data-target="#carouselHand" data-slide-to="1"></li>
            <li data-target="#carouselHand" data-slide-to="2"></li>
            <li data-target="#carouselHand" data-slide-to="3"></li>
        </ol>
        <!-- Wrapper for slides -->
        <div class="carousel-inner">
            <div class="carousel-item active">
                <img class="d-block w-100 portfolioImgWide" src="../img/portfolio/hand/Glove.jpg" alt="Glove">
                <div class="carousel-caption">
                    <p>Flex-sensing Glove</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="carousel-item">
                <img class="d-block w-100 portfolioImgWide" src="../img/portfolio/hand/Hand.jpg" alt="Printed Hand">
                <div class="carousel-caption">
                    <p>3D printed Hand</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="carousel-item">
                <img class="d-block w-100 portfolioImgWide" src="../img/portfolio/hand/hand.gif" alt="Printed Hand">
                <div class="carousel-caption">
                    <p>3D Model of Hand</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="carousel-item">
                <img class="d-block w-100 portfolioImgWide" src="../img/portfolio/hand/finger.gif"
                        alt="Printed Hand">
                <div class="carousel-caption">
                    <p>3D Model of A Finger</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <!-- Left and right controls -->
        <a class="carousel-control-prev" href="#carouselHand" role="button" data-slide="prev">
            <span class="carousel-control-prev-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
            <span class="sr-only">Previous</span>
        </a>
        <a class="carousel-control-next" href="#carouselHand" role="button" data-slide="next">
            <span class="carousel-control-next-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
            <span class="sr-only">Next</span>
        </a>
    </div>

    <div class="portfolio-description">
        <p> My goal was to make a robotic hand, that would mimic the movements of the user. I designed and 3D
                    printed this hand. Each finger of the hand is controlled by a servo, attached by fishing line. Due
                    to time constraints and shipping delays, I also designed the flex sensors seen on the glove; these
                    were made with conductive foam and pieces of yogurt containers, as the resistance of the conductive
                    foam changes as pressure is applied. The microcontroller measures the amount of this change, and
                    adjusts the fingers accordingly. I had worked with <a href="https://ericschilha.github.io">Eric
                      Schilha</a> on this project.</p>
        <p> The technical report for this project can be read <a
                      href="../img/portfolio/hand/Technical_Report.pdf" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">here </a>
        </p>
        <p>The video below shows my robotic hand, mimicking the movements of the user wearing the flex-sensor
                    glove I created.</p>
        {{ iframeVideo("J854ql37A94") }}
        <p></p>
        {{ iframeVideo("w7eW1fjC244") }}
        <p>Above is a demo video of the pre-programmed gestures I have put on the robotic hand.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="text-center">
        <ul class="list-inline">
            <li>
                <a href="https://github.com/AbhinavA10/CHRPMini-Hand" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Github Repo</a>
            </li>
            <li>Timeframe: Grade 11</li>
            <li>Relevant Technologies: C, Fusion360</li>
        </ul>
        <a  href="../projects.html">
            <button class="btn btn-primary" type="button">
                <i class="fa fa-times"></i>
                  Close Project
            </button>
        </a>
    </div>
{% endblock %}